{"type":"article","id":9910,"title":"【加速】荷兰战线后续：学校组织香港问题讲座，粉红留学生计划抱团前去高唱国歌","uid":8201,"topics":[2942,2933,91,37,17],"contents":"前情提要：格罗宁根大学校报事件（<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/9718\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pincong.rocks/article/9718</a>）发酵大成功，在reddit和原文评论区都引发了舆论彻底反转。学校还进一步决定组织关于香港的讲座和纪录片欣赏活动：<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://sggroningen.nl/evenement/hong-kongs-protests-and-its-future?language_content_entity=und&amp;lang=en\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://sggroningen.nl/evenement/hong-kongs-protests-and-its-future?language_content_entity=und&amp;lang=en</a><br>\n<br>\n部分粉红留学生看到之后立刻开始崩溃+无能狂怒，截取部分脑瘫发言：<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/EXXqd89.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/EXXqd89.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/EXXqd89.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/4QEISfO.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4QEISfO.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/4QEISfO.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/E3mZ1p9.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/E3mZ1p9.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/E3mZ1p9.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/WFY5zfx.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WFY5zfx.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/WFY5zfx.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/RAomQdS.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RAomQdS.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/RAomQdS.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/5rS4pJo.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/5rS4pJo.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/5rS4pJo.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n到这里其实已经几乎不需要我们加速了，这些小粉红已经完美展示了它们的形象。不过还是希望各位手足帮忙：<br>\n1. 能否转发到连登，看看有没有当地的香港留学生？鉴于会场很可能有小粉红前来闹事或者「辩论」然后发视频回墙内，能有提前了解情况的人在场当然是最好的。<br>\n2. 荷兰人制作了一整部关于香港的纪录片（<a href=\"https://www.vpro.nl/programmas/tegenlicht/kijk/afleveringen/2019-2020/hongkongs-nieuwe-helden.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.vpro.nl/programmas/tegenlicht/kijk/afleveringen/2019-2020/hongkongs-nieuwe-helden.html</a>），这次在格罗宁根播出后还会到荷兰各地巡展，有在欧洲的或许可以考虑参与线下聚会？<br>\n3. 给主办方写信或者社交媒体留言，表达感谢并提醒小粉红可能的威胁。主办方的邮箱是：studium@rug.nl，在本次活动的页面最下方还有他们的<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/studiumgeneralegroningen/\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">fb</a>、<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SGGroningen\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">twitter</a>链接等。<br>\n<br>\n活动页面：<a href=\"https://sggroningen.nl/evenement/hong-kongs-protests-and-its-future?language_content_entity=und&amp;lang=en\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://sggroningen.nl/evenement/hong-kongs-protests-and-its-future?language_content_entity=und&amp;lang=en</a>","date":"2019-11-30","agreeCount":22,"discussionCount":0}